Hi Amanda,


Thanks for the email.


It appears that the Aviso website is not authenticated to send as wordpress@avisowa.com.au or website@avisowa.com.au. This is by design so that someone can't just pose as a trusted Aviso WA sender. For me to fix this, we will need to update the website's email sending server with an authenticated one.


Did you have access to the WordPress site? If so, I can update the settings from our end. Otherwise, I can provide some details so your web developer can add them instead.


I just released a couple of emails from quarantine; One being an account setup email from the WordPress site, the other a website enquiry. You would have just received these.


Also, I noticed that the team@avisowa.com.au only consists of yourself. Is this expected?


Please let me know and I can go from there. 😊


Kind regards,​
​
